Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.83,0:00:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在忍者的世界裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.47,0:00:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不遵守規則和破壞紀律的傢伙被稱為廢物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.70,0:00:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊 不懂得珍惜同伴的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.92,0:00:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才是最差勁的廢物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.31,0:00:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距今數十年前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.06,0:00:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍者五大國的統治發生了動搖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.88,0:00:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在各國的國境附近
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.33,0:00:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小國以及忍者村的小型衝突頻繁爆發
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.38,0:00:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長期的戰爭讓木葉也出現了大規模的傷亡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.21,0:00:43.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是後世所稱的「第三次忍界大戰」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.10,0:00:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推算出敵人增援力量的關鍵後
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.53,0:00:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,控制住這裡是重中之重
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.95,0:00:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神無毗橋…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.52,0:01:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須立刻制定摧毀此處的作戰計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.39,0:01:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在各地戰火肆虐的現今
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.96,0:01:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能派出少數精兵完成此次任務
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.84,0:01:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任命上忍波風皆人 旗木卡卡西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.96,0:01:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇智波帶土以及凜四人行動
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.91,0:01:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃色閃光就不用說了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.56,0:01:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但其他人都太年輕了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.64,0:01:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常時期要用非常手段啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.56,0:01:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是迫不得已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.85,0:03:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.83,0:03:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去會被殺的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.51,0:03:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來得及嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.83,0:03:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕上了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.17,0:03:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 你遲到了 帶土
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.18,0:03:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道集合時間到底是幾點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.82,0:03:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然成為了能獨當一面的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.35,0:03:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵守約定和規則就是理所當然的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.13,0:03:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.26,0:03:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,途中被一位提著行李 步履蹣跚的老太太拉著問路
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.83,0:03:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且眼睛裡進了灰塵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.11,0:03:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 這些都是謊言吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.38,0:04:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別那麼說嘛 卡卡西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.37,0:04:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶土陪老太太一起走了 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.61,0:04:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還幫忙提行李了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.79,0:04:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師太老實了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.92,0:04:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總不會每次都有需要幫助的人出現在帶土面前吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.21,0:04:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不遵守規則和紀律的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.25,0:04:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為忍者會被稱為廢物的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.51,0:04:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.51,0:04:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的內心就沒有一絲柔情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.74,0:04:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是說什麼規則紀律 煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.77,0:04:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的是自制力才對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.46,0:04:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了 你們倆都別吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.18,0:04:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說也是同一隊的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.21,0:04:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜 你也太寵帶土了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.75,0:04:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天對於我而言可是相當重要的日子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.66,0:04:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也…也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.59,0:04:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼日子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.07,0:04:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從今天起 卡卡西跟我一樣是上忍了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.41,0:04:53.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了提高執行任務時的效率
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.67,0:04:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我決定和卡卡西班分成兩組行動
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.99,0:05:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為木葉的戰鬥力從未像如今這麼不足過
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.28,0:05:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分開行動的話 那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.56,0:05:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.41,0:05:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡卡西擔任隊長 帶領帶土和凜三人一隊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.99,0:05:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我則是一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.25,0:05:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這之前不是已經商量過了嗎 帶土
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.04,0:05:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要送卡卡西禮物的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.12,0:05:20.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我沒聽見
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.00,0:05:25.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就送你這個吧 特製的苦無
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.65,0:05:27.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然稍微有點沉 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.47,0:05:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但習慣了就會覺得很好用的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.50,0:05:31.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.82,0:05:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我準備的 給
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.20,0:05:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,個人用的特別醫療包
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.47,0:05:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了能夠方便使用 已經全部改良過了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.49,0:05:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.71,0:05:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼意思啊 這隻手…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.12,0:05:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本沒東西要送你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.86,0:05:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 也沒什麼大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.40,0:05:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正你送的東西也沒什麼用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.66,0:05:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的東西只會成為累贅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.98,0:06:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說真的 你這種人能當上上忍真是不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.78,0:06:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還輪不到你來說我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.47,0:06:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是宇智波一族的宇智波帶土啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.88,0:06:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天會超越你的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.56,0:06:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我的寫輪眼開眼之後
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.97,0:06:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇智波一族不都是精英嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.21,0:06:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不依賴那種東西也應該很厲害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.97,0:06:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.88,0:06:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…你們別再吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.29,0:06:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該說明一下任務的內容了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.38,0:06:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經接近國境了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.54,0:06:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看好了 就是這條線
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.85,0:06:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是現在土之國侵略草隱村的進攻路線
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.73,0:06:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然敵人就是巖忍村的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.87,0:06:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據情報顯示 敵人的前線已經有數千名忍者了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.54,0:06:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰線比之前又推進了好多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.13,0:06:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟火之國與草隱村相互接壤
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.80,0:06:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著挨揍就太晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.35,0:07:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人的推進如此順利…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.34,0:07:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就表示他們後方的支援非常順暢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.26,0:07:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此 這次的任務就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.27,0:07:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神無毗橋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.86,0:07:15.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在最前線迎擊敵人需要大量的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.67,0:07:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我們這些進行阻礙工作的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.42,0:07:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須由少數精銳組成
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.10,0:07:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.92,0:07:27.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 是潛入任務了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.59,0:07:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡卡西隊的任務就是潛入敵人的後方區域
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.31,0:07:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破壞這座用於物資供給的橋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.36,0:07:39.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切斷敵人的援助機能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.48,0:07:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後迅速撤離
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.07,0:07:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.70,0:07:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會直接去前線阻擊敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.91,0:07:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也順便為你們誘敵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.77,0:07:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 今天卡卡西就是隊長了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.63,0:07:58.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到國境之前我會同你們一起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.84,0:08:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後就分頭行動 開始執行任務
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.48,0:08:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得好 卡卡西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.12,0:08:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被發現了嗎 真是些厲害的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.40,0:08:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.97,0:08:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…怎麼會…應該不可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.92,0:08:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 先觀察一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.66,0:08:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一個人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.40,0:08:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家小心 敵人有二十個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.09,0:08:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是影分身
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.86,0:08:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來的確如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.38,0:08:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師…我要衝上去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.13,0:08:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請掩護我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.88,0:08:50.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衝動是魔鬼啊 卡卡西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.23,0:08:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是負責殿後吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.84,0:08:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師 今天我是隊長吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.93,0:09:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正打算試一下開發中的新術呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.55,0:09:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要衝過來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.00,0:09:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.38,0:09:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事 這個術…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.11,0:09:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多麼驚人的查克拉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.98,0:09:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.76,0:09:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便大量敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.02,0:09:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個術也能一瞬間解決他們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.43,0:09:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就如同老師的綽號一樣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.24,0:09:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.39,0:09:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師…您也說過了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.11,0:09:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我是隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.05,0:09:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊伍中要服從隊長的命令是規定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.84,0:09:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.12,0:09:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到居然會這樣直接衝過來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.63,0:09:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛的苦無讓我確認了所有人的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.30,0:09:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.46,0:09:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.22,0:10:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 影分身嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.49,0:10:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 下一個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.37,0:10:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別大意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.34,0:10:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第十八個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.96,0:10:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別太囂張了 小子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.57,0:10:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡卡西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.61,0:10:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然能勉強針對那個小鬼的攻擊進行反擊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.08,0:10:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是那金髮混蛋的動作就…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.71,0:10:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經附上印記了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.26,0:11:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師的瞬身之術 好快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.81,0:11:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說 你就是那位木葉的黃色閃光
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.56,0:11:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我們的巖隱村…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.25,0:11:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長官曾告誡過 如果遇到那傢伙就趕緊跑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.36,0:11:21.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這話的意思我總算是明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.81,0:11:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡卡西受的傷也不輕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.53,0:11:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫且從這裡撤退 重整隊形吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.67,0:11:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.87,0:11:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會沒事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.53,0:11:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變成這樣都是因為你不聽老師勸的緣故
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.63,0:11:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還輪不到你來教訓我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.12,0:11:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛嚇得在一邊哭出來的宇智波精英
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.99,0:11:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那只是眼睛被灰塵迷到才流淚的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.46,0:11:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍者心得 第二十五條知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.77,0:11:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「忍者不可以流淚」這一條
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.55,0:12:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個都別吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.64,0:12:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我適可而止吧 你們兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.66,0:12:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡卡西 規則和紀律的確很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.26,0:12:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那並不是一切
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.58,0:12:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.11,0:12:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有需要根據實際情況隨機應變的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.17,0:12:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 你看吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.12,0:12:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶土 你也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.21,0:12:26.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴著護目鏡是不可能有灰塵迷到眼睛的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.92,0:12:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自制力不能光掛在嘴上說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.70,0:12:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要讓自己的心靈變得更加堅強才是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.33,0:12:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一點 卡卡西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.19,0:12:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那個術還是不要再用了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.97,0:12:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看得出 那是集中於一點的刺擊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.52,0:12:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確有著相當的破壞力和速度
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.15,0:12:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是也會因為自己的移動速度過快
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.84,0:12:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而無法看清楚對方的反擊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.36,0:12:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個並不成熟的術
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.95,0:12:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分開之前 我再重申一次
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.92,0:13:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對忍者而言 最重要的就是團隊合作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.55,0:13:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.90,0:13:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.92,0:13:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也知道團隊合作的重要性
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.90,0:13:28.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.59,0:13:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡卡西那傢伙總把我看成一無是處的笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.83,0:13:34.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.36,0:13:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我出身於被稱作精英的宇智波一族
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.88,0:13:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻總是個吊車尾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.10,0:13:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也承認卡卡西非常厲害 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.58,0:13:51.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡卡西是被稱為木葉白牙的天才忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.74,0:13:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旗木佐久茂先生的兒子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.06,0:13:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在他的父親面前 連傳說的三忍也要敬他幾分
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.03,0:14:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那種天才的身邊度過了童年
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.72,0:14:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到你們時有所失落 也是很正常的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.26,0:14:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白牙…這個名字我也聽說過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.41,0:14:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說是為了保護村子而殉職的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.69,0:14:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡卡西那傢伙 從來都沒說過這些啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.59,0:14:25.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村子裡的人 當然包括卡卡西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.37,0:14:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都尊敬著這位了不起的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.54,0:14:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到那個事件的發生…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.54,0:14:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事件
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.83,0:14:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事或許不該由我擅自說出來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.07,0:14:42.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你既然跟卡卡西是隊友 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.22,0:14:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是想讓你知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.53,0:14:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.33,0:14:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡卡西的父親佐久茂先生因為遭到中傷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.94,0:14:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而親手終結了自己的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.70,0:14:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五年前 在執行某極秘任務時 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.99,0:15:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為隊長潛入敵方陣營的他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.66,0:15:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在被迫面對兩個選擇時
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.53,0:15:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是執行任務 還是解救夥伴的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.79,0:15:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然 根據村裡的規定 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.66,0:15:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放棄任務是不允許的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.68,0:15:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 他為了挽救夥伴的性命而選擇中斷任務
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.33,0:15:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 因此而蒙受了巨大損失的火之國
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.27,0:15:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及村裡的夥伴們都開始指責他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.80,0:15:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最終 甚至連被他救回的夥伴也中傷他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.76,0:15:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐久茂先生因此身心俱疲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.81,0:15:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而後就自行…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.38,0:15:46.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那以後 卡卡西就不再提及父親的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.76,0:15:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且十分執著於遵守規則和約定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.70,0:15:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶土 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.16,0:16:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕一點點也好 你就稍微體諒他一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.51,0:16:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡卡西沒有惡意的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.63,0:16:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經好很多了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.33,0:16:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過太勉強的話 傷口可會裂開哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.85,0:16:19.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該上路了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.50,0:16:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從現在起兵分兩路
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.61,0:16:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.46,0:16:29.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的敵人只是偶爾單獨出來偵察的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.33,0:16:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後面就會變成團隊作戰了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.38,0:16:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要多加小心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.04,0:16:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快上路吧 隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.29,0:16:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.14,0:16:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散開
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.13,0:16:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 魔蛭那傢伙出去偵察後就沒回來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.19,0:17:03.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該不會是被那些小鬼給幹掉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.43,0:17:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問問他們不就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.69,0:17:07.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍法.迷彩隱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.02,0:17:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火遁.豪火球之術
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.34,0:17:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙就交由我們來看管了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.71,0:17:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.57,0:17:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.09,0:18:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶土 不要追那些傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.45,0:18:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.92,0:18:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道自己說了些什麼嗎 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.22,0:18:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們兩個繼續執行任務
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.53,0:18:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜呢 那凜怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.48,0:18:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜之後再想辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.51,0:18:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人想要知道我們的作戰計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.04,0:18:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會馬上殺了她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.39,0:18:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且幸運的是 凜是個醫療忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.44,0:18:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使成為俘虜也不會被虧待
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.20,0:18:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要答應治療敵人的傷員
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.38,0:18:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.03,0:18:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人更想瞭解我們的作戰內容
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.89,0:18:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦情報洩漏的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.55,0:18:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們就會馬上加強對橋的戒備吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.65,0:18:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話 完成任務便會更加困難
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.10,0:18:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說凜能平安無事完全是自己的想像吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.39,0:18:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的那些傢伙如果是些笨蛋嘍囉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.63,0:18:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又會如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.43,0:18:57.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今 比起完成任務 解救凜才是優先事項
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.91,0:19:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍者即便是犧牲夥伴也要完成任務
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.49,0:19:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是規定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.56,0:19:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這項任務如果失敗了 戰爭將會延長
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.60,0:19:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許會有更多的犧牲者出現
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.28,0:19:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一切都只是假設而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.44,0:19:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道因為這個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.92,0:19:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就輕易地捨棄一直出生入死的夥伴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.67,0:19:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次你我受傷的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.65,0:19:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜總是以醫療忍術救我們的命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.88,0:19:28.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒有她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.09,0:19:31.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你我怕是早就死了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.37,0:19:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也只是凜的任務而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.40,0:19:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然我還是討厭你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.61,0:19:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭我也沒關係 我才是隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.97,0:19:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要聽從我的指示  
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.19,0:19:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論在什麼情況下  
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.99,0:19:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了避免小隊四分五裂 決策人只有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.92,0:19:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才會規定隊員應當服從隊長的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.07,0:19:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶土 你沒有能力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.07,0:20:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才會成為這個隊的隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.93,0:20:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那為什麼不去救凜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.12,0:20:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是有能夠解救同伴的能力嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.36,0:20:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果一時感情用事而導致重要的任務失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.35,0:20:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後肯定會後悔莫及的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.20,0:20:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才會有忍者必須消除感情的規定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.82,0:20:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也應該明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.29,0:20:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜…凜可是因為擔心你才會送你醫療包的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.74,0:20:36.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在包的內側還縫製了護身符
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.77,0:20:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫療包和醫療忍術都是為了提升任務的成功率
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.18,0:20:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而由木葉想出的出色體系
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.47,0:20:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 昨天我也跟你說過了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.29,0:20:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的東西反而會成為累贅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.56,0:20:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.34,0:21:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍者需要的只是對於任務有用的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.01,0:21:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感情什麼的 都是沒用的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.21,0:21:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.78,0:21:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的這麼認為嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.71,0:21:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.26,0:21:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.83,0:21:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你我本來就水火不容
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.99,0:21:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去救凜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.73,0:21:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你根本就什麼都不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.63,0:21:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,違反規定的傢伙會怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.07,0:22:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為白牙是真正的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.72,0:22:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確 在忍者的世界裡  
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.16,0:22:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,違反規則和紀律的傢伙會被稱為廢物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.63,0:22:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.10,0:22:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不珍惜夥伴的傢伙是更差勁的廢物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.49,0:22:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正都是廢物 那麼我選擇打破規則
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.82,0:22:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果說因此不能算是忍者的話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.29,0:22:30.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那忍者之類的 就由我來打倒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.05,0:23:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可終於來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.31,0:23:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.65,0:23:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵方估計有五十人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.91,0:23:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我方僅我們四人存活
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.02,0:23:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就能見分曉了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.95,0:23:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家要一鼓作氣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.85,0:23:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 請將這些苦無都擲向敵方陣營內
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.46,0:23:30.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後就交給我一個人來辦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.49,0:23:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太亂來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.29,0:23:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎麼說 一個人也…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.62,0:23:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴 照他說的做
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.93,0:23:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來就能欣賞木葉黃色閃光的戰鬥了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.66,0:23:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只在一瞬之間 可不能錯過哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.62,0:24:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經好很多了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.42,0:24:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是太勉強的話 傷口會裂開的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.70,0:24:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次你我受傷的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.69,0:24:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜總是用醫療忍術救我們的命
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.74,0:24:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒有她
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.03,0:24:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你我怕是早就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.73,0:24:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此刻比起完成任務
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.24,0:24:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解救凜才是優先事項
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.15,0:24:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,規則和紀律的確很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.60,0:24:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那並不是一切
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.90,0:24:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.52,0:24:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有需要根據實際情況隨機應變的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.34,0:24:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為白牙是真正的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.96,0:24:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確 在忍者的世界裡 
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.80,0:24:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,違反規則和紀律的傢伙會被稱為廢物
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.11,0:24:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.31,0:24:56.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不珍惜夥伴的傢伙是更差勁的廢物
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.76,0:25:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.43,0:25:15.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜 我也能做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.59,0:25:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去收拾那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.75,0:25:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這段時間 你就繼續使用幻術
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.01,0:25:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快把情報打探出來
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.07,0:25:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷彩隱之術
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.57,0:25:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.01,0:25:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算去哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.67,0:26:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡…卡卡西
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.48,0:26:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.38,0:26:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總不能把事情交給你這種愛哭鬼忍者獨自去辦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.65,0:26:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡卡西
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.00,0:26:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銀白色的頭髮 
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.38,0:26:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上那綻放白光的查克拉刀…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.77,0:26:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.39,0:26:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木葉的白牙
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.10,0:26:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我父親的遺物
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.32,0:26:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍者需要的只是對任務有用的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.70,0:26:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感情什麼的 都是沒用的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.64,0:26:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡卡西 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.90,0:26:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 白牙的小孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.44,0:26:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就沒什麼好怕的了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.09,0:26:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.03,0:26:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氣味完全消除掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.24,0:26:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能從微弱的空氣流動和聲音中
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.62,0:26:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來判斷敵人的位置了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.21,0:26:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪…在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.82,0:27:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶土 後面
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.03,0:27:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.37,0:27:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡卡西
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.51,0:27:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡卡西 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.47,0:27:23.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使對手是些小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.22,0:27:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要謹慎才是
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.21,0:27:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是穩紮穩打地上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.74,0:27:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人…真不簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.60,0:27:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經將沾有我血腥味的苦無給丟掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.02,0:27:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛裡又進灰塵了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.97,0:27:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍者是不能哭的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.19,0:27:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒死 可不要掉以輕心了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.96,0:27:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴著護目鏡是不可能有灰塵跑進眼睛的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.24,0:27:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自制力不能光掛在嘴上說說
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.21,0:27:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要讓自己的心靈變得更加堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.75,0:28:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只會逞口舌之快
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.34,0:28:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還總是讓大家來幫助我
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.52,0:28:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個只說不做的吊車尾
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.54,0:28:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.66,0:28:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為白牙是真正的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.46,0:28:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不珍惜夥伴的傢伙是更差勁的廢物
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.80,0:28:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有這番話 我不想只停留在口頭上
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.98,0:28:30.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.41,0:28:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為…為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.08,0:28:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明明不可能看到我的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.43,0:28:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶土 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.28,0:28:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼 這雙眼睛…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.93,0:28:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在 輪到我來保護夥伴了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.50,0:29:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶土 你的眼睛…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.46,0:29:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來這就是寫輪眼
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.86,0:29:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能看清查克拉形成與流向
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.76,0:29:19.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧 卡卡西
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.18,0:29:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來我的左眼不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.27,0:29:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有凜送我的這個
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.54,0:29:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能立刻做應急處理
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.89,0:29:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快去救凜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.70,0:29:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是意外地難纏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.93,0:29:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是些沒有用的東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.97,0:30:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜的查克拉流向有些紊亂
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.41,0:30:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你我的不同
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.41,0:30:11.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是被施加了幻術
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.87,0:30:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是想立刻問出情報啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.96,0:30:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來不是普通的小鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.36,0:30:22.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟他交手過 他的速度很快
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.12,0:30:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多加小心
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.86,0:31:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.13,0:31:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡卡西
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.46,0:31:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶土
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.03,0:31:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們來救你了 
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.36,0:31:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜 已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.33,0:31:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 接下來就趕快撤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.24,0:31:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.81,0:31:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說配合很不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.27,0:31:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但畢竟還是小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.90,0:31:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在你們可還是處於敵人的手心之中啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.15,0:31:32.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土遁.巖屋崩落
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.61,0:31:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.86,0:31:38.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快往出口跑
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.75,0:31:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡卡西
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.14,0:32:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是得來不易的情報源
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.00,0:32:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這也沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.10,0:32:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.94,0:32:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜 卡卡西
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.56,0:32:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶土
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.32,0:32:38.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別白費力氣了 卡卡西
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.56,0:32:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…好像已經不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.08,0:32:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右半身幾乎都被壓爛了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.23,0:32:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連感覺都沒有了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.00,0:32:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.49,0:33:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…怎麼會…為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.43,0:33:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶土
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.77,0:33:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.68,0:33:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我…如果我一開始就照你說的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.81,0:33:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起來救凜的話
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.07,0:33:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不會變成這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.89,0:33:31.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還算什麼隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.81,0:33:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算什麼上忍
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.79,0:33:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.98,0:33:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我差點忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.72,0:33:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.58,0:33:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒給慶祝你升為上忍的禮物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.47,0:33:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡卡西…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.17,0:33:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該給你什麼呢…我有考慮過
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.79,0:34:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在…終於想到了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.21,0:34:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.94,0:34:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是什麼無用的累贅
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.09,0:34:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要把我的寫輪眼送給你
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.75,0:34:26.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管村裡的人怎麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.34,0:34:30.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都是個了不起的上忍
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.97,0:34:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.19,0:34:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就收下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.08,0:34:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜 用你的醫療忍術
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.15,0:34:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我的寫輪眼連同眼軸一起移植到卡卡西的左眼處
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.83,0:34:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡卡西 到這裡來
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.12,0:34:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.90,0:35:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就要…死了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.14,0:35:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我會成為你的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.78,0:35:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為你看清未來的
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.26,0:35:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真難纏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.92,0:35:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.36,0:35:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過…小鬼就是小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.59,0:35:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為忍者怎麼能哭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.11,0:35:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 愛哭鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.81,0:35:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們做個了斷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.68,0:36:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個小鬼 好像跟剛才不太一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.66,0:36:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡卡西 凜就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.94,0:37:12.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用緊張 凜
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.84,0:37:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡卡西 快點…帶著凜從這裡離開
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.90,0:37:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人的援軍…就要來了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.66,0:37:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶土
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.99,0:37:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.11,0:37:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.42,0:37:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土遁.裂土轉掌
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.32,0:38:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜 快抓住我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.43,0:38:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.57,0:38:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶土
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.63,0:38:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易和卡卡西那傢伙搞好了關係
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.80,0:38:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最終還是沒能向凜告白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.79,0:38:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希望能繼續跟大家在一起啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.04,0:38:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶土
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.44,0:39:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.25,0:39:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶土 這是你幫我完成的術
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.98,0:39:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種狀況下還有跟我們戰鬥的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.72,0:39:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是敢於潛入敵人後方的人
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.72,0:39:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好勝心真強
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.44,0:39:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜 這些傢伙由我來擋住
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.25,0:39:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁機逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.46,0:39:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.26,0:39:47.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶土把你托付給我
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.25,0:39:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我就算死也會保護你的
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.06,0:39:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡卡西
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.46,0:39:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜 帶土喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.99,0:39:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.61,0:40:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別珍惜你
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.35,0:40:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.37,0:40:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拼上性命也要保護你
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.40,0:40:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼卡卡西 我的心情也…
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.61,0:40:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.50,0:40:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是個曾經一度想棄你不顧的人渣
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.07,0:40:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走 凜
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.22,0:40:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…死了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.42,0:40:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.20,0:40:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你終於醒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.34,0:40:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.53,0:40:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.15,0:40:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這把苦無上的術式 
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.09,0:41:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為了讓我用時空間忍術進行移動的標記
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.66,0:41:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…敵人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.11,0:41:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都被我打倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.57,0:41:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜呢 凜在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.93,0:41:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒能及時趕到真是很抱歉 卡卡西
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.99,0:41:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情我都從凜那裡聽說了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.51,0:41:37.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三次忍界大戰
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.28,0:41:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這場曠日持久的戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.88,0:41:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伴隨著眾多無名忍者的犧牲宣告終結
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.09,0:41:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與此同時 
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.09,0:41:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也成就了無數英雄流芳百世的傳說
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.50,0:41:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神無毗橋之戰
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.86,0:41:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.93,0:42:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木葉誕生了兩位擁有寫輪眼的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.42,0:42:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中一人的名字被刻在了慰靈碑上
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.73,0:42:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而另一人則被稱為「寫輪眼卡卡西」
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.70,0:42:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其名聲更是響徹他國
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.73,0:43:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活捉宇智波鼬
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.81,0:43:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是要完成這個任務
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.14,0:44:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用一般的方法可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.04,0:44:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 這件事我無論如何也不能迴避
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.08,0:44:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了帶回佐助嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.67,0:44:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.24,0:44:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是現在佐助已經有了能打倒大蛇丸的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.25,0:44:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.22,0:44:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.23,0:44:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一向言出必行
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.45,0:44:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我的忍道
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.63,0:44:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.51,0:44:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始行動的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.20,0:44:42.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為火影忍者誕生10週年的紀念作品
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.72,0:44:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劇場版最新作終於公映了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.42,0:44:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算會破壞規定
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.66,0:44:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要救出老師
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.49,0:44:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劇場版火影忍者疾風傳
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.86,0:44:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火之意志的繼承者
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.49,0:44:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木葉村面臨第四次忍界大戰的危機
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.22,0:44:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了保護心愛的村子
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.66,0:45:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壯烈的戰鬥現在開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.99,0:45:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劇場版最新作
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.28,0:45:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,8月1日終於公映
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.58,0:45:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我們的火之意志
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.20,0:45:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粉絲們在街上等待著最新作
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.60,0:45:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般在公映之前
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.90,0:45:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東京都內會組織成品試映會
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.75,0:45:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會場裡聚集了久等這天的大量粉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.02,0:45:22.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全場超級滿員哦
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.58,0:45:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 在最新作上演之前展開的舞台問候
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.26,0:45:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有豪華的陣容登場哦
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.89,0:45:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以鳴人為首
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.20,0:45:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聲優們 監督都陸續出場
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.87,0:45:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會場氣氛非常熱烈
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.48,0:45:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.41,0:45:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.95,0:45:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是飾演漩渦鳴人的竹內順子
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.90,0:45:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天雖然時間不多
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.82,0:45:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還請大家好好享受 這之後還有電影呢
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.01,0:45:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次上舞台 很緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.60,0:45:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實呢 我今天是來調查小姐三圍的
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.98,0:46:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣 請好好享受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.82,0:46:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旁邊也有小姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.53,0:46:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旁邊也有小姐呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.32,0:46:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.97,0:46:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個 那個 舞台問候真的很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.95,0:46:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這之後
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.35,0:46:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電影會怎麼樣開始呢
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.55,0:46:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有多少幸福和心跳的感覺彙集上來
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.05,0:46:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.32,0:46:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.17,0:46:24.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.26,0:46:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.07,0:46:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.78,0:46:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熱鬧的舞台問候之後 最新作終於開始上映
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.83,0:46:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還問了大家很多觀後感哦
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.67,0:46:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.42,0:46:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太精彩了 全部都很帥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.14,0:46:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火影忍者的劇場版最棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.77,0:46:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木葉的各位最棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.10,0:46:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 以後還要多多關照啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.56,0:46:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木葉村面臨第四次忍界大戰的危機
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.59,0:47:01.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了保護心愛的村子
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.31,0:47:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼承火之意志的人們集合
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.75,0:47:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壯烈的戰鬥現在開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.03,0:47:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為火影忍者誕生10週年的紀念作品
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.80,0:47:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即將播出劇場版火影忍者疾風傳
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.31,0:47:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火之意志的繼承者
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.65,0:47:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,8月1日終於公映了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.43,0:47:17.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我們的火之意志
